This paper focuses on the practical usage of deterministic regular expressions (DREs) in XML and schema data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL), Databases (cs.DB), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper involves data collection, analysis, and practical applications, which are relevant to these sub-categories.
